<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> kopparakecari paṉ
<lb n="2"/>makku cellāniṉṟa yāṇṭu
<lb n="3"/>Irupattāṟāvatu kāṭaṉ pūtimāṇik
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kaṉ makaḷ muṇṭaṅkoṉai cātti
<lb n="5"/>tiruceṅkoṭṭu tiruvātirai kaṇaperumakkaḷ
<lb n="6"/>kaiyyil vaitta poṉ Aiṅkaḻañcu Ippoṉṉiṉ palicai
<lb n="7"/>koṇṭu Aivar <hi rend="grantha">brāhma</hi>ṇarai cantirātittaval Ūṭṭuvomā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṉom tiruvātirai kaṇaperumakkaḷom [ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> *]
